OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,FA rapist who attacked a university
OL,7,Ffresher nearly 50 years ago has been
OL,8,Fjailed after he was caught using
OL,9,Fadvances in DNA techniques.
OL,11,FThe 18-year-old victim, who had
OL,12,Farrived as a student in Leeds on the
OL,13,Fday of the incident in October 1977,
OL,14,Fawoke to find masked David Sharp
OL,15,Fbreaking in through her bedroom window
OL,16,Fbefore he assaulted her.
OL,18,FSharp was only arrested after a review
OL,19,Fof the case by West Yorkshire Police
OL,20,Fcold case detectives in 2023. He was
OL,21,Fconvicted of rape last month.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,FConfronting her attacker in court on
OL,7,FThursday as he was jailed for six
OL,8,Fyears, the woman said it was the first
OL,9,Ftime she had ever seen Sharp's face.
OL,11,FShe told the 66-year-old he was a
OL,12,F"delusional, cowardly individual who
OL,13,Fis cruel to the core".
OL,15,F"I have carried the events of that
OL,16,Fnight in my head for almost 49 years,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,F"It has dominated my life. There is
OL,7,Fnot a day that passes that it does not
OL,8,Frun through my mind like a horror film
OL,9,Fon continual repeat."
OL,11,FSharp avoided capture for more than
OL,12,Ffour decades until the case was looked
OL,13,Fat again in 2023.
OL,15,FDNA taken at the time of the incident
OL,16,Fdid not match anyone on the national
OL,17,Fprofile database.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,FBut further enquiries led to a match
OL,7,Fwith one of Sharp's relatives and a
OL,8,Fsample taken from him proved he was
OL,9,Fthe culprit.
OL,11,FOfficers later confirmed Sharp, now of
OL,12,FCopland Meadows, Totnes, Devon, was
OL,13,Fliving in Leeds at the time of the
OL,14,Foffence.
OL,16,FIn a victim impact statement, the
OL,17,Fwoman told Sharp: "For the first time
OL,18,Fin 49 years, you are no longer in
OL,19,Fcontrol of this situtation."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,FShe said: "My heart aches for that
OL,7,Fyoung woman. It was to be the start of
OL,8,Fme being more independent, spreading
OL,9,Fmy wings and exploring the city of
OL,10,FLeeds and the world. I had such
OL,11,Fenormous hope, potential and the world
OL,12,Fto explore. This was all stolen away
OL,13,Ffrom me that night.
OL,15,F"Years later, I reflect on that time
OL,16,Fin October 1977 and think of my poor
OL,17,Fparents who left me in Leeds that
OL,18,Fnight, believing that I was safe from
OL,19,Fharm.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,F"Never could they have imagined that
OL,7,Fsuch a horrendous act would befall
OL,8,Ftheir youngest daughter."
OL,10,FSharp will be on the Sex Offenders
OL,11,FRegister for life and was given a
OL,12,Flifetime restraining order.
OL,14,FDet Insp Stephen King, of West
OL,15,FYorkshire Police, paid tribute to the
OL,16,F"incredibly courageous" victim.
OL,18,FHe added: "She is at the centre of
OL,19,Fthis investigation into events which
OL,20,Fscarred her whole adult life and until
OL,21,Fnow remained unresolved.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,364,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1776971469
OL,3,CRapist jailed over 1977 attack on
OL,4,Cuniversity fresher
OL,6,F"No prison sentence can make up for
OL,7,Fthe ongoing trauma that the victim has
OL,8,Fendured over 48 years and the way it
OL,9,Fmapped her life."
OL,11,FHe added that forensic science was
OL,12,F"continually developing" and would be
OL,13,Fused to re-examine other unsolved
OL,14,Fcrimes.
OL,16,FLast month, 75-year-old David Hill was
OL,17,Fjailed for the knifepoint rape of a
OL,18,Fwoman in Sheffield city centre in
OL,19,FSeptember 1985 after he was also
OL,20,Fcaught by a cold case team using
OL,21,Fadvanced DNA methods.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
